 Project 3: Blog Platform (Backend)

Today's Focus: Complete Backend Development
What I Built: Full-featured blog platform backend with:

User authentication (JWT)

CRUD operations for blog posts

Comment system

Like/dislike functionality

Category management

Image upload for posts

Search functionality

API Endpoints Created:

POST /api/auth/register

POST /api/auth/login

GET /api/posts (with pagination)

POST /api/posts (with image upload)

PUT /api/posts/:id

DELETE /api/posts/:id

POST /api/posts/:id/comments

POST /api/posts/:id/like

Tech Stack: Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose, JWT, Multer


